Split record values by language.

@param record: a record from PS
@param fields: fields whitelist
@return a dictionary with the following structure:

    'en_US': {
        'field1': value_en,
        'field2': value_en,
    },
    'it_IT': {
        'field1': value_it,
        'field2': value_it,
    }
